The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 12 December 2010


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

In a powerful live broadcast, Alex will run the gammet from Wikileaks to the economy. The arrest of Wikileaks founder Julian Assange has sparked what some hacker groups are referring to as the first global cyber war.
